  "George took over his family's Kaiser-Francis Oil Company in the 1960s.",
  "Kaiser bought Bank of Oklahoma in 1991 for $60 million; he owns about 54% of the publicly-traded bank.",
  "Kaiser has donated more than $4 billion to his charitable foundations, which focus on early childhood education.",
  "In 2018 Kaiser opened The Gathering Place, a 66-acre park in Tulsa that's the largest public park in the country built with private funds.",
  "In the 1930s Kaiser's parents fled Nazi Germany and settled in Tulsa, Oklahoma."
